{"tid":2334162,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"四人被控去年於黃埔參與非法集結 嚴舜儀裁定三人罪名不成立 一人罪名成立","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T10:02:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"919c76bfeecc32ab959454bf5e63d618447d12f1","tid":2334162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12276&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=a747ae50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12276</a><br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官<br />\n#1027黃埔<br />\n#裁決<br />\n<br />\n👥傅,林,袁,* <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1) #非法集結 [D1-D4]<br />\n2) 管有 #攻擊性武器 (鐵鎚仔) [D1]<br />\n3-6) 4項 #蒙面法 [D1-D4]<br />\n<br />\n速報<br />\nD1 ‼️所有罪名成立‼️<br />\nD2 D3 ❌所有罪名不成立❌<br />\nD4 ❌所有罪名不成立❌<br />\n<br />\n早休，之後聽取求情。<br />\nD1暫不還押，但不能離開法庭。"},{"pid":"df1c3a14f88dd22bdb06d22681f68d027684f24e","tid":2334162,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"恭喜D2 3先<br />\nD1手足要撐落去啊"},{"pid":"b176ec4944e5f22442ccf686c461680e622c1e55","tid":2334162,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"佢判唔入真係鳩咬"},{"pid":"5a1224d92e4e894ae8b3d799c9686c4aaa0de791","tid":2334162,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"d1入晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b94de6eaa0a9ee4dfe1b6a8e587be6142768cb5","tid":2334162,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" cl