有攻擊性武器罪成。嚴官再指警員或錯認第2、3被告，而且不能排除有其他人當日與第4被告衣著打扮接近，故裁定其餘3名被告非法集結及期間使用蒙面物品罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"c7abd80a7f52f88f798e78e242a032127d94295e","tid":2334162,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b059f895ffc5f38ec49702c321c2c13f9a1fe9","tid":2334162,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068f9b084719d359e7228798c97c4aebe4cc401c","tid":2334162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eded2907e45365e477adf9e60f2f2b7f4b24462f","tid":2334162,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"想知詳細"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"去年10月27日在尖沙咀「追究警暴、連繫穆斯林」集會後各區爆發警民衝突，4名學生在紅磡被警員截查時搜出口罩及錘，被控非法集結、使用蒙面物品等 6 罪。裁判官嚴舜儀今早在九龍城裁判法院裁定案發當日現場屬非法集結，接納警員證供指首被告當時身處聚集人群之中，並拒絕接納其辯解當日正打算用膳和帶錘子回工作室配合鉚釘加工時裝，裁定首被告非法集結、期間使用蒙面物品及管有攻擊性武器罪成。嚴官再指警員或錯認第2、3被告，而且不能排除有其他人當日與第4被告衣著打扮接近，故裁定其餘3名被告非法集結及期間使用蒙面物品罪名不成立。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978a817bebd3349626a12a83a37a3fc9ed9c829a","tid":2334162,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"之前新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/EBLSNWPITFBSHHJHWI7JFJW5PA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FEBLSNWPITFBSHHJHWI7JFJW5PA%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=10e55b13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FEBLSNWPITFBSHHJHWI7JFJW5PA%2F&h=a74e4709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/EBLSNWPITFBSHHJHWI7JFJW5PA/</a>"},{"pid":"63a7244bd80ec0d00a33ee215f330d1422c008f3","tid":2334162,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:21:2